Motormaster lands, looking at the two bots he dosent know. He looked as if
he was triying to restrain something. "My name is Motormaster" He stammers.
My crew and I were shot down by enemy ships and we are stranded here. Could
you provide us with some help?" He finishes with a look of discust on his
face. How long can I keep this whiny attitude up, He thinks to himself.
